author: jmachols
msg: These classes really belong here within the the server test project rather
than the ldapd-test project since it is dependent on server classes and
interfaces.  If we keep it in ldapd-test then ldapd-test will be dependent
on ldapd-server and ldapd-common-test which depends on ldapd-test will then
depend on ldapd-server indirectly through the dependency on ldapd-test.
